      "text": [
        "٤٤٤. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): قَلِيلٌ مَدُومٌ عَلَيْهِ خَيْرٌ مِنْ كَثِيرٍ مَمْلُولٍ مِنْهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "444. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: A little that lasts is better than much that brings grief."
